WEBVTT

00:00.683 --> 00:03.641
Madrid is your first stop in experiencing...

00:03.706 --> 00:06.353
...the Spanish love affair with art and expression.

00:06.850 --> 00:09.425
From the nation's greatest painters and writers...

00:09.799 --> 00:12.531
...to iconic European works in every medium,...

00:12.895 --> 00:15.413
...Madrid's museums must not be missed.

00:16.133 --> 00:19.917
Explore the heritage of the Spanish people to prehistoric times...

00:20.334 --> 00:24.848
...with ancient artifacts housed in elaborately decorated noble palaces...

00:25.167 --> 00:26.284
...and mansion houses...

00:26.568 --> 00:29.783
...or take a look into Spain's military and colonial history.

00:30.134 --> 00:32.423
Take in the city's contemporary galleries...

00:32.570 --> 00:35.747
...or pick up a discount museum pass for added savings.

